Package fr.uge.patchwork.model

Record Class Piece

java.lang.Object
java.lang.Record
fr.uge.patchwork.model.Piece
Record Components:
schema - : diagram of the piece
cost - : cost of the piece
time - : time to place the piece
button - : presence of a button on the piece
public record Piece(ArrayList<ArrayList<Boolean>> schema, int cost, int time, int button) extends Record
Class dedicated to the representation of a piece (or a "patch" of the game).
